PrecisAuthority to execute and issue an Instrument of RATIFICATION OF THE LEGALLY BINDING STATEMENT issued by Canada at a meeting of the Joint Consultative Group of the Conventional Armed Forces in Europe (CFE), which acknowledged the legally binding statement made at the same meeting by the UNIONS of the Soviet Socialist Republics, with respect to the application of provisions of the Treaty on Conventional Armed Forces in Europe (CFE) as regards the Baltic States, Estonia, Latvia, and Lithuania.
